This package was created by Andy Mortimer <andy.mortimer@zetnet.co.uk>
based on the packaging put together by Larry Daffner <vizzie@airmail.net>,
with help from Wichert Akkerman <wakkerma@wi.leidenuniv.nl>.

Based on the package for svgalib 1.2.8 by Richard Kettlewell,
based on Ted Hajek's original Debian package.
Then maintained by Lenart Janos <ocsi@debian.org>,
followed by Guillem Jover <guillem@debian.org>.

It was downloaded from <http://www.svgalib.org/>.

